OL,3,CJersey nurses raise 'safe staffing'
OL,4,Cand housing as top concerns
OL,6,F"Safe staffing" and housing are the
OL,7,Fpredominant concerns of Jersey nurses,
OL,8,Faccording to the head of the UK's
OL,9,Flargest nursing union.
OL,11,FProfessor Nicola Ranger, General
OL,12,FSecretary and Chief Executive of the
OL,13,FRoyal College of Nursing (RCN), has
OL,14,Fvisited the island to speak to nurses
OL,15,Fworking in Jersey's health department.
OL,17,FIt is the first time in over 20 years
OL,18,Fthat an RCN General Secretary has made
OL,19,Fsuch a trip.
