OL,3,CJersey nurses raise 'safe staffing'
OL,4,Cand housing as top concerns
OL,6,FProfessor Ranger says it is essential
OL,7,Fto hear from nurses first-hand,
OL,8,Fexplaining: "We can't be someone's
OL,9,Fvoice if you don't listen to them.
OL,11,F"It's really important I hear directly
OL,12,Ffrom nurses what they're worried
OL,13,Fabout, what they're proud of, what
OL,14,Ftheir concerns are, because it's very
OL,15,Funique wherever you go."
OL,17,FProfessor Ranger says the biggest
OL,18,Fsurprise was that earnings were not
OL,19,Fthe chief concern for the island's
OL,20,Fnurses.
