OL,3,CJersey nurses raise 'safe staffing'
OL,4,Cand housing as top concerns
OL,6,FShe adds: "I would say that when it
OL,7,Fcomes to anywhere else I go, pay is
OL,8,Fdominant, but it isn't dominant here.
OL,9,FThey feel that the pay is fair and
OL,10,Fthat's great, although they recognise
OL,11,Fit's an expensive place to live and
OL,12,Fwork.
OL,14,F"Safe staffing and having enough staff
OL,15,Fwith the right skills is something
OL,16,Fthat they are talking about in every
OL,17,Fsetting because that's really vital
OL,18,Ffor patients and the people they're
OL,19,Fcaring for.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
