OL,3,CJersey nurses raise 'safe staffing'
OL,4,Cand housing as top concerns
OL,6,F"They're not saying that things are
OL,7,Funsafe, but they need to know they've
OL,8,Falways got enough nurses, 24 hours a
OL,9,Fday, seven days a week, and sometimes
OL,10,Fthey feel a little more stretched than
OL,11,Fothers.
OL,13,F"The other predominant concern is
OL,14,Fhousing and accommodation when you
OL,15,Ffirst come over, because rents are
OL,16,Fhigh.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
