OL,3,CJersey nurses raise 'safe staffing'
OL,4,Cand housing as top concerns
OL,6,F"There have been discussions about
OL,7,Fthat crossover between deciding to
OL,8,Flocate permanently or get on that
OL,9,Fhousing ladder, and I know there is a
OL,10,Freal focus on trying to make that
OL,11,Fbetter and easier for people.
OL,13,FThe RCN head says progress is being
OL,14,Fmade, explaining: "I can see,
OL,15,Fparticularly in the hospital setting,
OL,16,Fa real sense of trying to expand the
OL,17,Fnumber of homegrown nurses.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
