OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F382A1753654494
OL,3,CJersey nurses raise 'safe staffing'
OL,4,Cand housing as top concerns
OL,6,F"A really good plan around that is
OL,7,Fchanging to a different university
OL,8,Fprovider, and they've been able to
OL,9,Fincrease the number of people training
OL,10,Fto be nurses; I think that's a really
OL,11,Fgood model."
OL,13,FWhen asked whether improvements have
OL,14,Falso been made following a review
OL,15,Fthree years ago that criticised the
OL,16,Fhealth service as "potentially unsafe"
OL,17,Fdue to allegations of bullying,
OL,18,FProfessor Ranger says: "We haven't
OL,19,Fheard about a bullying culture
OL,20,Fdirectly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
