OL,3,CJersey nurses raise 'safe staffing'
OL,4,Cand housing as top concerns
OL,6,F"Some members have felt things could
OL,7,Fget better in some areas, and we will
OL,8,Fwork with the organisation to make
OL,9,Fsure that happens.
OL,11,F"Leadership teams at the hospital and
OL,12,Fother organisations are very cognizant
OL,13,Fof that, but creating a culture where
OL,14,Fpeople feel they can raise concerns
OL,15,Fcan be more challenging in a more
OL,16,Fintimate environment."
