OL,3,CJersey nurses raise 'safe staffing'
OL,4,Cand housing as top concerns
OL,6,FProfessor Ranger says she has been in
OL,7,Fconversation with Jersey's Health
OL,8,FMinister, Deputy Tom Binet, about the
OL,9,F"real challenges" facing the island's
OL,10,Fhealthcare.
OL,12,FShe adds: "We talked about genuinely
OL,13,Fputting patients at the centre and how
OL,14,Fwe could design things to make sure
OL,15,Fthat patients are genuinely well
OL,16,Flooked after.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
