OL,3,CJersey nurses raise 'safe staffing'
OL,4,Cand housing as top concerns
OL,6,F"It's important that the constant
OL,7,Fpresence for many patients - whether
OL,8,Fthey're in their home or in hospital -
OL,9,Four nursing staff has to be brilliant
OL,10,Fand keep people safe and cared for."
OL,12,FProfessor Ranger also reported a "real
OL,13,Fexcitement" about the development of a
OL,14,Fnew hospital, explaining: "I think
OL,15,Fit's been welcomed.
OL,17,F"We know the amount of energy and time
OL,18,Fit takes to build a new hospital, so
OL,19,Fit's vital that there's focus on other
OL,20,Fareas of care, which need to remain,
OL,21,Fsuch as the hospice and community care.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
